{
  "stem": "9701.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know whether I would risk my life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Fortunately, I've never been put to that task.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so with that, the hatred across the board against the adult German population, it just-- it's vanished.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's gone.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In fact, in 1991, I was in Germany on a speaking tour.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And after one of my presentations, a couple of people told me afterwards, you're much too forgiving of Germans.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I said to them, you know, I don't know you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Why should I hate you?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And even if you've done some despicable thing, let's talk about it, why you did it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Let me understand why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I know I didn't finish one trend of thought.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After my contract with the Censorship division expired, or even prior to that, I applied-- I decided I wanted to stay in Germany longer.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I applied for a position with the Nuremberg Trial, with the-- not with the international trial, but with the-- what was called the subsequent proceedings, which were conducted by the American government in the same Palace of Justice in Nuremberg where the international trial took place.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were 12 such trials.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was assigned to the trial of the doctors who performed medical experiments on concentration camp inmates.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my job was to look for the documentary evidence used in the trial.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I would spend most of my time in Berlin in a former Nazi document center, which was located in Dahlem, D-A-H-L-E-M, which is a suburb of Berlin.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This document center was very deep under the ground.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was operated by the American Army.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there was an American colonel by the name of Helms, H-E-L-M-S, who was in charge of that document center.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
